{"tid":625472,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)追魂交易 真實謊言 極盜戰","createTime":"2018-04-11T13:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T19:08:37.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"863ad474ad07b1ff4b382777fd3fd95e4a0caa4b","tid":625472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=60IjaljOmdVCL6an69oRXU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e856d726\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=60IjaljOmdVCL6an69oRXU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=7e699abf\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/3f/Devilsadvocate.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F3f%2FDevilsadvocate.jpg&h=842a0842&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/94/True_Lies.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F94%2FTrue_Lies.jpg&h=875f314e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/0d/Den_of_Thieves_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F0d%2FDen_of_Thieves_Poster.jpg&h=903b5e7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.由泰勒&middot;哈克佛執導，艾爾&middot;帕西諾、基努&middot;李維及莎莉&middot;賽隆等主演。電影改編自Andrew Neiderman的同名小說，描述一名鄉鎮律師被邀到紐約工作後，怪事連連發生的故事<br />\n<br />\n2.哈里（阿諾&middot;史瓦辛格飾演）是一名隸屬於美國國家安全情報組織「奧米加局」（Omega Sector）的資深超級特工，精通多國語言並且擁有高技術性的間接手段。哈里及他的同伴們正接受了一個重大任務------調查1個名為「紅蓮聖戰」的恐怖主義組織所策劃的私運核彈頭並於美國發動襲擊的案件。任務期間他認識了「紅蓮聖戰」的重大幹部------表面為古玩商人的朱諾，並為了查緝需要而接近她。基於國家安全問題<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述一群劫匪盯上了美國聯準會所管理的龐大金錢，而計劃了一場搶劫行動以企圖將其奪為己有。這個劫匪組織早已被洛杉磯警察局菁英部門的警探尼克鎖定，並打算將他們在奪取這鉅款前逮捕歸案，這使得這群劫匪想要使計劃成功幾乎是件不可能的任務...<br />\n<br />\n9 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=60IjaljOmdVCL6an69oRXU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=0d879a2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=60IjaljOmdVCL6an69oRXU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=bbbee097\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a24d415015ea7d2080859554f4bee4fab7343d7","tid":625472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87275cf519763cba4dcfea8f7a34f8a8875bdf1e","tid":625472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc82c42b9266c077a9351c36396ce71c5